48:["$","p",null,{"className":"x:not-first:mt-[1.25em] x:leading-7","children":[["$","code",null,{"className":"nextra-code","dir":"ltr","children":"plane-mcp-server"}]," is configured in Ava’s ",["$","code",null,{"className":"nextra-code","dir":"ltr","children":".mcp.json"}],". All agents running on the Ava host inherit 55+ Plane MCP tools covering issues, cycles, modules, members, states, and projects. This allows agents to read and write Plane data directly as tool calls without going through the webhook flow."]}]
